Day 1 :
  Steps to create basic django project:

1.	Install python
2.	Install Django
        ---------------------------------
        |	Command : pip install django  |
        ---------------------------------

# To create a New project using django :
	    ---------------------------------------------------
      | Command : django-admin startproject projectName |
      ---------------------------------------------------

#To run a  created project you can use following 
    command :First of all go to particular path where you created your django project and the use following :
    -----------------------------------------
    |  command: python manage.py runserver |
    -----------------------------------------

#To change a port you have to use command are as follow:
  ---------------------------------------------------
  | Command : python manage.py runserver portnumber |
  ===================================================
